@Comment:	Time is 0:04
@Comment:	MOT says she usually reads to Chi and Chi names some words; EXP suggests that Chi tell the story by the pictures , which she starts out doing; Mot at one point asks <who else reads this to ya>; I think she's referring to something other than other visits; sometime during the fruit pages Chi asks Mot to read some; Chi does contribute a lot to the telling though. Mot handles Chi well. She clearly distinguishes reading from talking by intonation , and she asks Chi a few questions but doesn't push her too far. EXP is ready to stop after Mot gets a brief phone call , but Mot and Chi want to continue. Chi's affect is a little startling , but I expected it , sort of like DEB
